name:                DHT-Node-Example
version:             0.1.0.0
synopsis:            Example of using DHT.Node
description:         Run several DHT.Node's (which makes the choice of using UDP,MVars,DHT.Routing and in memory Maps to store data)
                     to test storing and looking up data and neighbours.
